(1, 'uoLUixdbmyfu5Jgp5izQysIbPNzGEBS4TR7Kd5Az.jpg', '{\"en\":\"Learn and grow!\",\"az\":\"\\u00d6yr\\u0259n v\\u0259 inki\\u015faf et!\"}', '{\"en\":\"You are in a great place to develop yourself!!\",\"az\":\"\\u00d6z\\u00fcn\\u00fc inki\\u015faf etdirm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\u0259la bir yerd\\u0259s\\u0259n!\"}', '{\"en\":\"Learn with us!\",\"az\":\"Biziml\\u0259 \\u00f6yr\\u0259n!\"}', '{\"en\":\"<div>Digiuth is an online learning platform that helps the youth discover and develop their youth work, interpersonal, business, education, technology-related, and creative skills through video courses prepared by young professionals. The platform has been created within \\u201cDigital Transformation in the Youth Sector: Experience of Visegrad Countries\\u201d project. Meanwhile, \\\"Development of the Digiuth Online Learning Platform with Experience of V4 Countries\\\" project is a follow up project of the previous one with an aim of increasing number of courses offered on the platform. The project is coordinated by Erasmus Student Network Azerbaijan and co-financed by the Governments of Czechia, Hungary, Poland and Slovakia through Visegrad Grants from International Visegrad Fund. The mission of the fund is to advance ideas for sustainable regional cooperation in Central Europe. Digiuth aims to improve the digital learning resources of the youth and youth organizations by partnering with experienced organizations of V4 group of countries. &nbsp;<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>Digiuth, g\\u0259nc m\\u00fct\\u0259x\\u0259ssisl\\u0259rin haz\\u0131rlad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 onlayn kurslar vasit\\u0259sil\\u0259 g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r\\u0259 sosial i\\u015f, g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rl\\u0259 i\\u015f, biznes, texnologiya, t\\u0259hsil v\\u0259 yarad\\u0131c\\u0131l\\u0131q sah\\u0259l\\u0259rind\\u0259 bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131n\\u0131 k\\u0259\\u015ff etm\\u0259y\\u0259 v\\u0259 inki\\u015faf etdirm\\u0259y\\u0259 k\\u00f6m\\u0259k ed\\u0259n onlayn \\u00f6yr\\u0259nm\\u0259 platfo