priate tunes when you shouldn\'t. It also directly ties into emotional awareness, or the ability to identify personal experiences, which can be a protective factor against psychopathology by allowing an individual to recognize the need to activate appropriate emotion regulation strategies.<br><br><\\\\\\/div><div>Experiments were conducted on seven young people with symptoms of depression. I don\'t want to bother you with unnecessary details so I will cut to two main sections of the experiments. (you can read the whole experiment <a href=\\\\\\\"https:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/www.frontiersin.org\\\\\\/articles\\\\\\/10.3389\\\\\\/fpsyg.2019.01199\\\\\\/full\\\\\\\">here<\\\\\\/a>)<br><br><\\\\\\/div><div><br><\\\\\\/div>\\\"}\"}'),
