(327, '95ff369f-930f-4417-8556-75a8ece00e21', 33, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\Team', 4, 'App\\Models\\Team', 4, 'App\\Models\\Team', 4, '', 'finished', '', '2022-04-06 08:27:36', '2022-04-06 08:27:36', NULL, '{\"image\":\"z11XRNkIYaBE0p5Iu2m7rtIy4oVpBEPogSgkbSWs.jpg\",\"fullname\":{\"en\":\"Etibar Khidirov\",\"az\":\"Etibar X\\u0131d\\u0131rov\"},\"position\":{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"<div><strong>Etibar Khidirov<\\/strong> is a graduate of Khazar University\'s Faculty of Economics and Management.&nbsp; Since his university years, he has served as a volunteer and volunteer coordinator at many major forums and events in the country.&nbsp; In addition, he was an active participant and organizer of many social projects.&nbsp; Participation in social projects later aroused interest in Social Entrepreneurship and he began to take an interest in and research in this area.&nbsp; When he was in his 4th year, he started his career as a project manager at Toxum.org, the country\'s first crowdfunding platform based on the Social Entrepreneurship model.&nbsp; After getting acquainted with social entrepreneurship, Etibar saw that this field coincides with his personal values, which makes him happy.&nbsp; And his goal was to build his own social entrepreneurship project to benefit society more.&nbsp; And finally, in 2022, Etibar achieved its goal.&nbsp; Destekchi.org has established the Social Entrepreneurship Platform, which will support social and social entrepreneurship projects in the country to meet their resource needs.&nbsp; Future plans of the Etibar are to contribute as much as possible to the newly developed field of social entrepreneurship in Azerbaijan and to support those who want to start in this field.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>Etibar X\\u0131d\\u0131rov&nbsp; X\\u0259z\\u0259r Universitetinin \\u0130qtisadiyyat v\\u0259 menecment&nbsp; fakult\\u0259si m\\u0259zunudur. Universitet ill\\u0259rind