(419, '9602a456-7600-4586-aeb6-8dfd294301b5', 52, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 16, 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 16, 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 16, '', 'finished', '', '2022-04-08 01:21:52', '2022-04-08 01:21:52', NULL, '{\"image\":\"fM8zi93knn78a2tHE3ymjf4txVpYBtNuMX0cnyPx.jpg\",\"fullname\":{\"en\":\"Etibar Khidirov\",\"az\":\"Etibar X\\u0131d\\u0131rov\"},\"position\":{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"},\"content\":{\"az\":\"<div>Etibar X\\u0131d\\u0131rov&nbsp; X\\u0259z\\u0259r universitetinin \\u0130qtisadiyyat v\\u0259 Menecment&nbsp; fak\\u00fclt\\u0259si m\\u0259zunudur. Universitet ill\\u0259rind\\u0259n \\u00f6lk\\u0259d\\u0259 h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7iril\\u0259n bir \\u00e7ox b\\u00f6y\\u00fck forum v\\u0259 t\\u0259dbirl\\u0259rd\\u0259 k\\u00f6n\\u00fcll\\u00fc v\\u0259 k\\u00f6n\\u00fcll\\u00fcl\\u0259r \\u00fczr\\u0259 koordinator kimi f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259tl\\u0259ri olub.&nbsp; Bundan \\u0259lav\\u0259, bir \\u00e7ox sosial layih\\u0259l\\u0259rin aktiv i\\u015ftirak\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131 v\\u0259 t\\u0259\\u015fkilat\\u00e7\\u0131lar\\u0131ndan biri olmu\\u015fdur.&nbsp; Sosial layih\\u0259l\\u0259rd\\u0259 i\\u015ftirak onda daha sonra sosial sahibkarl\\u0131\\u011fa maraq oyatm\\u0131\\u015f v\\u0259 bu sah\\u0259 \\u00fczr\\u0259 maraqlanma\\u011fa v\\u0259 ara\\u015fd\\u0131rmalar etm\\u0259y\\u0259 ba\\u015flam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.&nbsp; El\\u0259 ilk karyeras\\u0131na da 4-c\\u00fc kursda t\\u0259hsil alark\\u0259n Sosial Sahibkarl\\u0131q Modeli \\u0259sas\\u0131nda f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259r\\u0259n \\u00f6lk\\u0259nin ilk kraudfandinq platformas\\u0131 Toxum.org-da layih\\u0259l\\u0259r \\u00fczr\\u0259 menecer kimi ba\\u015flam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Etibar sosial sahibkarl\\u0131qla tan\\u0131\\u015f olduqdan sonra bu sah\\u0259d\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmaqdan z\\u00f6vq ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n h\\u0259m\\u00e7inin, bu sah\\u0259nin \\u015f\\u0259xsi d\\u0259y\\u0259rl\\u0259ri il\\u0259 \\u00fcst-\\u00fcst\\u0259 d\\u00fc\\u015fd\\u00fcy\\u00fcn\\u00fcn f\\u0259rqin\\u0259 vard\\u0131 . N\\u0259hay\\u0259t, 2022-ci ild\\u0259 Etibar \\u00f6z\\u00fcn\\u00fcn bu m\\u0259qs\\u0259dini realla\\u015fd\\u0131rd\\u0131. \\u00d6lk\\u0259d\\u0259 olan sosial v\\u0259 sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q layih\\u0259l\\u0259rinin resurs ehtiyac\\u0131n\\u0131 qar\\u015f\\u0131lamaqda onlara d\\u0259st\\u0259k olacaq \\\"D\\u0259st\\u0259k\\u00e7i\\\" (Destekchi.org) Sosial Sahibkarl\\u0131q Platformas\\u0131n\\u0131 qurdu.&nbsp; Etibar\\u0131n g\\u0259l\\u0259c\\u0259k planlar\\u0131 Az\\u0259rbaycanda yeni inki\\u015faf etm\\u0259y\\u0259 ba\\u015flayan sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q sah\\u0259si \\u00fczr\\u0259 bacard\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 q\\u0259d\\u0259r \\u00f6z t\\u00f6hf\\u0259sini verm\\u0259k v\\u0259 bu sah\\u0259y\\u0259 ba\\u015flamaq ist\\u0259y\\u0259nl\\u0259r\\u0259 d\\u0259st\\u0259k olmaqd\\u0131r. Az\\u0259rbaycandak\\u0131 sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q il\\u0259 maraqlananlara t\\u00f6hv\\u0259 verm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn Digiuth proyekti \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u201cSosial sahibkarl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n \\u0259saslar\\u201d adl\\u0131 video d\\u0259rslik haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>Etibar Khidirov is a graduate of Khazar University\'s faculty of Economics and Management.&nbsp; Since his university years, he has served as a volunteer and volunteer coordinator at many major forums and events in the country.&nbsp; In addition, he was an active participant and organizer of many social projects.&nbsp; Participation in social projects later aroused interest in Social Entrepreneurship and he began to take an interest in and research in this area.&nbsp; When he was in his 4th year, he started his career as a project manager at Toxum.org, the country\'s first crowdfunding platform based on the Social Entrepreneurship model.&nbsp; After getting acquainted with social entrepreneurship,&nbsp; his goal was to build his own social entrepreneurship project to benefit society more. Etibar achieved his goal in 2022.&nbsp; Destekchi.org has established the Social Entrepreneurship Platform, which will support social entrepreneurship projects in the country to meet their resource needs.&nbsp; Future plans of the Etibar are to contribute as much as possible to the newly developed field of social entrepreneurship in Azerbaijan and to support those who want to start in this field. He has developed a video lesson&nbsp; entitled \\\"Fundamentals of Social Entrepreneurship\\\" as part of the Digiuth project to contribute to those interested in social entrepreneurship in Azerbaijan.<\\/div>\"},\"linkedin_link\":null,\"facebook_link\":null,\"instagram_link\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2022-04-08T01:21:52.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-04-08T01:21:52.000000Z\",\"id\":16}'),
(420, '9602a498-2bbb-4b0d-a197-1563b9ee4be4', 52, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 17, 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 17, 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 17, '', 'finished', '', '2022-04-08 01:22:35', '2022-04-08 01:22:35', NULL, '{\"image\":\"iQRYWBCbtZDmdYvgEIhk4rmKBqxufZuPpH6AdO6m.jpg\",\"fullname\":{\"en\":\"Fidan Ahmadli\",\"az\":\"Fidan \\u018fhm\\u0259dli\"},\"position\":{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"<div>Fidan Ahmadli graduated from the lyceum named after Academician Zarifa Aliyeva in 2015. She is a graduate of ADA University\'s Faculty of Computer Engineering. In 2019, she won the Erasmus + program and continued her education at Istanbul City University for 1 semester in January-May. In 2018, she won the Global Startup Lab program held by MIT University in Azerbaijan and participated in 6-week startup training organized by MIT. Fidan has many certifications, including \\u2018Oracle Certified Associate\\u2019. During her university years, she has participated in many internship programs, including Azersun Holding, TelecomInvest companies. Since September 2020, she has been working at Azerconnect LLC as a specialist in IT Corporate Platforms. Fidan prepared \\u201cIntroduction to SQL\\u201d video lessons for the Digiuth platform.<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div><strong>Fidan \\u018fhm\\u0259dli<\\/strong> 2015-ci ild\\u0259 Akademik Z\\u0259rif\\u0259 \\u018fliyeva ad\\u0131na liseyden m\\u0259zun olmu\\u015fdur. O, ADA universitetinin Komp\\u00fcter M\\u00fch\\u0259nd\\u0259sliyi fak\\u00fclt\\u0259si m\\u0259zunudur. 2019-cu ild\\u0259 Erasmus+ proqram\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak etm\\u0259 haqq\\u0131 qazanm\\u0131\\u015f v\\u0259 h\\u0259min proqram \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 yanvar-may aylar\\u0131 \\u0259rzind\\u0259 1 semestr boyunca \\u0130stanbul \\u015eehir Universitetind\\u0259 t\\u0259hsilini davam etdirmi\\u015fdir. 2018-ci ild\\u0259 Amerikan\\u0131n MIT Universitetinin Az\\u0259rbaycanda ke\\u00e7irdiyi \\u201cGlobal Startup Lab\\u201d proqram\\u0131n\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak haqq\\u0131 qazanaraq, MIT t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n t\\u0259\\u015fkil olunan 6 h\\u0259ft\\u0259lik startup t\\u0259liml\\u0259rind\\u0259 i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. Fidan, \\u2018Oracle Certified Associated\\u2019 daxil olmaqla, bir \\u00e7ox sertifikatlar\\u0131n sahibidir. Universitet ill\\u0259ri boyunca \\u201cAzersun Holding\\u201d, \\u201cTelecomInvest\\u201d \\u015firk\\u0259tl\\u0259ri daxil olmaqla bir \\u00e7ox t\\u0259cr\\u00fcb\\u0259 proqramlar\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. 2020-ci ilin Sentaybr ay\\u0131ndan etibar\\u0259n \\u201cAzerconnect\\u201d MMC-d\\u0259 IT Korperativ platformalar\\u0131 \\u00fczr\\u0259 m\\u00fct\\u0259x\\u0259ssis olaraq f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259rir. Digiuth platformas\\u0131 \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn is\\u0259 \\u201cSQL-\\u0259 giri\\u015f\\u201d adl\\u0131 video d\\u0259rslik haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.<\\/div>\"},\"linkedin_link\":null,\"facebook_link\":null,\"instagram_link\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2022-04-08T01:22:35.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-04-08T01:22:35.000000Z\",\"id\":17}'),
