eras\\u0131na yeni ba\\u015flatan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r\\u0259 d\\u0259st\\u0259k olmaq \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn Digiuth proyekti \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u201cU\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131 nec\\u0259 qurmal\\u0131?\\u201d adl\\u0131 video d\\u0259rsli haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>Laman Guliyeva is a graduate of Khazar University\'s Faculty of Psychology. During her university years, she organized many trainings and conferences, and later specialized in psychotherapy and psychological counseling. She is one of the team members of the \\\"Light\\\" start-up, which includes psychological and career tests, career planning, and a successful career choice. She has worked at the university on career development and planning, gaining knowledge and experience in the Human Resources departments of various companies such as GDG Professionals, and ABB Bank. She currently works in the training and development division of the HR. Her greatest interest is to create a supportive work environment, healthy relationships and high job satisfaction for people within the company. She has prepared a video lesson called \\\"How to Build a Successful Career?\\\" as part of Digiuth project in order to support young people who are just starting their careers.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\"},\"linkedin_link\":null,\"facebook_link\":null,\"instagram_link\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2022-04-08T01:25:29.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-04-08T01:25:29.000000Z\",\"id\":21}'),
