(453, '961ac07e-c6e2-4357-a655-c6c1a989c7f7', 52, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\BlogCategory', 6, 'App\\Models\\BlogCategory', 6, 'App\\Models\\BlogCategory', 6, '', 'finished', '', '2022-04-20 01:00:28', '2022-04-20 01:00:28', NULL, '{\"title\":{\"en\":\"Informative\",\"az\":\"\\u00d6yr\\u0259dici\"},\"updated_at\":\"2022-04-20T01:00:28.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-04-20T01:00:28.000000Z\",\"id\":6}'),
(454, '961ac184-dbb7-4c40-9198-fd8f6aeea3b4', 52, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\Blog', 3, 'App\\Models\\Blog', 3, 'App\\Models\\Blog', 3, '', 'finished', '', '2022-04-20 01:03:20', '2022-04-20 01:03:20', NULL, '{\"blog_category_id\":6,\"title\":{\"en\":\"How to spend your time productively during the corona quarantine?\"},\"image\":\"mnGjC7YGoSHBNeyiEsyEkYPmr3sMBa0JijyTxOdw.png\",\"tags\":\"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"productivity\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"quarantine\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"skills\\\"}]\",\"content\":\"<h4 style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">Because of the prophylactic measures taken to prevent the coronavirus, the quarantine was announced in all classes across Azerbaijan. You may think that this is also a perfect vacation from the stress of university life, hanging out with friends, and relaxing. In the meantime, free time during the break could be used to spend it more productively and efficiently. Below are some things to devote some time of your time during quarantine to:<\\/h4><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Apply for scholarships, as well as master programs.<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\"><strong><em>Have you ever considered studying abroad after graduation?<\\/em><\\/strong> If you ever thought about perfect timing to apply, it is now! For senior students, most of the applications for Master Degrees are still open. The deadline for universities abroad usually varies from March to June, depending on the country and the program you wish to apply. Non-senior students, or those who would like to study masters after some break, can also dedicate their time to the <strong><em>research<\\/em><\\/strong>. Devoting some hours to your applications, such as writing your motivation letter, researching the best universities and scholarships to apply, knowing the requirements or the deadlines will ease your job during the application process later on.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Get an internship<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">Internships are the best way to explore your interests, build valuable connections as well as determine the right career path for you. Also, most universities abroad and jobs require to have previous relevant experience. Thus, internships play a huge role in gaining practical work experience to add to your CV. Some platforms will help you to find an internship easily. Sites such as <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/buqelemun.com\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">buqelemun.com<\\/a>, <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/edumap.az\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">edumap.az<\\/a>, <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/edu-active.com\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">edu-active.com<\\/a>, and CareerLink are some of those portals to ease the research process.&nbsp; Some of them require to write a motivation letter, so the break is a great opportunity to devote your time!<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Learn another language<\\/strong>.<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">Whether you practice at home or outside, it is better to spare some time for learning a new language. It has a lot of advantages for yourself and your future career. The following websites are helpful to hone your foreign language skills:<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\"><strong><em>Duolingo, Babbel, Busuu, BBC Languages.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Indulge in hobbies or try a new skill.<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">Research shows that learning something new has powerful brain-boosting power. During the breaks, try to spend time to try new skills and hobbies. You could learn or hone your skills further like cooking, juggling, playing the ukulele, drawing, negotiating, positive thinking, yoga, dance, making an origami, or anything! You will stretch your mind in many ways, which will establish new connections in your brain. All for free thanks to the magical power of the internet! \\uf04a<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Learn online.<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\"><strong>Continuously improving your knowledge is always a good idea. Read a book, magazine, or just simply: read online. There are many online courses you can learn from, which also provides a certificate. <\\/strong><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.coursera.org\\/\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">Coursera<\\/a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.udemy.com\\/\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">Udemy<\\/a> offer various online courses, which will boost your knowledge in almost any area.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Plan your summer break<\\/strong>.<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">It is important to learn how you will spend your summer holidays. Perhaps an internship, work and travel, volunteering, or any project abroad would be a great idea to spend it productively.&nbsp; Most applications are still open for summer activities, so get the most out of holidays, research, and apply!<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Create a blog<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">Have you ever thought about starting your blog but never had the time? This break might be the exact time for it! You will improve your writing skills by taking time each day to write. Creating a blog will help you to explore a topic of interest and add valuable skills such as outlining, copywriting, proofreading, and editing. You can try to create a blog in <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/wix.com\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">wix.com<\\/a>, <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/wordpress.com\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">wordpress.com<\\/a>.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Establish a professional digital presence<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">Whether you are a senior student or just searching for new job opportunities, you would want to establish a professional website or show your work experience and skills via LinkedIn. Polish your website and LinkedIn account: keep your website or account clean and professional; a professional photo, as well as updated resume, will work ideally. Also, review and edit your social media accounts. Make sure that employers will see your best self.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Improve your physical and mental health<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">This \\u201choliday\\u201d is a great opportunity to start sleeping well, eating healthily, and exercising regularly. You can also try new types of exercises to make a healthy life more fun to achieve! Pilates, golf, outdoor yoga, is good types of sport to explore. Moreover, sparing some time for self-care is highly important. You can ensure your well-being by improving your habits, listening to yourself, meditation, drinking more water, and trying positive affirmations.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Clear<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">Make clearing process in your life. Give away books, files, clothes and other things you no longer use. If they are still usable and you do not need them, consider giving them to a local charity. Also, clear your wardrobe, desk, email inbox to get organized.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Study<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">As midterms are approaching, devote your time to actually study and organize notes for the upcoming exams! It is a good opportunity to get the desired grades after the breaks are over.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><ol><li><p><strong>De-stress, relax, and protect yourself!&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">Make sure you recharge since it will be intensive after the breaks are going to end. As prophylactic measures are being taken, it is better to stay more indoors and de-stress yourself from the daily overwhelmed schedule. If you need to go outdoors, do not forget to take care of yourself by following simple measures.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">(Maintan social distance. Do not touch your mouth, nose, and eyes. Cover your mouth and nose, especially when sneezing. Wash and sanitize your hands frequently.)<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"text-align: start\\\">We wish you a productive time!<\\/h2><p style=\\\"text-align: start\\\"><span>&nbsp;Written by Turkan Valizada: <\\/span><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"mailto:tvalizada@esn.az\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">tvalizada@esn.az<\\/a><span>&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"user_id\":\"52\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-04-20T01:03:20.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-04-20T01:03:20.000000Z\",\"id\":3}'),
