(463, '961ac5d8-23d2-49c7-b0b3-a563bd173bd0', 52, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\News', 4, 'App\\Models\\News', 4, 'App\\Models\\News', 4, '', 'finished', '', '2022-04-20 01:15:25', '2022-04-20 01:15:25', NULL, '{\"news_category_id\":4,\"title\":{\"en\":\"Meet our new trainer!\",\"az\":\"Yeni t\\u0259lim\\u00e7imiz il\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f olun!\"},\"image\":\"QDsykeXR3KHIY3NU5FCULDp1icbtM0WguiB8zAwZ.jpg\",\"tags\":\"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Trainer\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"IT\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Website design\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"HTML\\\"}]\",\"content\":\"<p>Meet our local trainer on \\\"Introduction to HTML\\\" Mr. Alizade!<\\/p><p>He is currently studying for a bachelor\'s degree in Information Technology at ADA University. As a result of his studies, Mr. Alizade has became more interested in front-end development and developed his HTML, CAS, JS skills. Within the Digiuth project Mr. Alizade has been trained on \\\"Delve into the World of IT\\\" and \\\"Build Your Own Website \\\" by our international experts. Mr. Alizade has prepared the online course entitled \\\"Introduction to HTML\\\" for the Digiuth platform during this project.<\\/p><p>The main reason that Tangiz Alizade joined the Diguth program was to develop his knowledge and skills in building a website and to help other people who are interested in this field. After participating in a two weeks training organized by the Digiuth team and mastering what to do, his interest in this field increased even more. One of the main things that excites him is that he thinks that his study materials will explain the front-end development to other  interested people in a broad and detailed way, and that people will use this information to acquire new knowledge and skills. Mr. Alizada is looking forward to the future opportunities that Diguth will create to the youth of Azerbaijan.<\\/p><p><\\/p>\",\"user_id\":\"52\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-04-20T01:15:25.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-04-20T01:15:25.000000Z\",\"id\":4}'),
