,\"en\":\"Mastering SQL is the first step to becoming an Oracle expert. This training course is suitable for database developers who have no experience with SQL or Oracle. This course covers the basics required for coding using SQL in the Oracle 19c Database environment. Throughout the training, you will learn in detail what you need to know to access the input and output data in the database tables, as well as how to change the data. Course demonstrates how to use SELECT statements, filter and sort rows, and how to model and build a related database. After completing this course, you will have the basic skills needed to work with SQL in a related database management system.\"},\"language\":\"Azerbaijani\",\"course_duration\":\"120\",\"section_count\":\"4\",\"lecture_count\":\"12\",\"image\":\"R3PMi7hWeRIT2ZJDmukKdKvB5ICx3b1vkIOGIk62.png\",\"tags\":\"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"SQL\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"programming\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"database\\\"}]\",\"content\":{\"az\":\"<div>SQL-in m\\u0259nims\\u0259nilm\\u0259si Oracle m\\u00fct\\u0259x\\u0259ssisi olmaq \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn ilk add\\u0131md\\u0131r. Bu t\\u0259lim kursu SQL v\\u0259 ya Oracle il\\u0259 he\\u00e7 bir t\\u0259cr\\u00fcb\\u0259si olmayan veril\\u0259nl\\u0259r bazas\\u0131 t\\u0259rtibat\\u00e7\\u0131lar\\u0131 \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn uy\\u011fundur. Bu kurs Oracle 19c Database m\\u00fchitind\\u0259 SQL-d\\u0259n istifad\\u0259 ed\\u0259r\\u0259k kodla\\u015fd\\u0131rma \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn t\\u0259l\\u0259b olunan \\u0259saslar\\u0131 \\u0259hat\\u0259 edir. T\\u0259lim boyunca veril\\u0259nl\\u0259r bazas\\u0131 c\\u0259dv\\u0259ll\\u0259rin\\u0259 daxil olan v\\u0259 \\u00e7\\u0131xan m\\u0259lumatlar\\u0131 \\u0259ld\\u0259 etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn bilm\\u0259li oldu\\u011funuz \\u015feyl\\u0259r, h\\u0259m\\u00e7inin m\\u0259lumatlar\\u0131 nec\\u0259 d\\u0259yi\\u015fdir\\u0259c\\u0259yiniz \\u0259trafl\\u0131 \\u015f\\u0259kild\\u0259 izah edilir.&nbsp; SELECT ifad\\u0259l\\u0259rinin nec\\u0259 istifad\\u0259 edilm\\u0259yi, s\\u0259tirl\\u0259ri s\\u00fczg\\u0259cd\\u0259n ke\\u00e7irilm\\u0259si v\\u0259 \\u00e7e\\u015fidl\\u0259nm\\u0259si, h\\u0259m\\u00e7inin \\u0259laq\\u0259li veril\\u0259nl\\u0259r bazas\\u0131n\\u0131n nece modelle\\u015fdirildiyi v\\u0259 qurulmas\\u0131 praktiki \\u015f\\u0259kild\\u0259 g\\u00f6st\\u0259rilir. Bu kursu bitirdikd\\u0259n sonra siz \\u0259laq\\u0259li veril\\u0259nl\\u0259r bazas\\u0131 idar\\u0259etm\\u0259 sistemind\\u0259 SQL il\\u0259 i\\u015fl\\u0259m\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn laz\\u0131m olan \\u0259sas bacar\\u0131qlara sahib olacaqs\\u0131n\\u0131z.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>Mastering SQL is the first step to becoming an Oracle expert. This training course is suitable for database developers who have no experience with SQL or Oracle. This course covers the basics required for coding using SQL in the Oracle 19c Database environment. Throughout the training, you will learn in detail what you need to know to access the input and output data in the database tables, as well as how to change the data. Course demonstrates how to use SELECT statements, filter and sort rows, and how to model and build a related database. After completing this course, you will have the basic skills needed to work with SQL in a related database management system.<\\/div>\"},\"updated_at\":\"2022-05-31T06:18:31.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-05-31T06:18:31.000000Z\",\"id\":65,\"rating\":\"0.00\"}'),
