(921, '96766ada-c803-4b45-b650-184b5d3238dd', 10, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\News', 6, 'App\\Models\\News', 6, 'App\\Models\\News', 6, '', 'finished', '', '2022-06-04 14:37:10', '2022-06-04 14:37:10', NULL, '{\"news_category_id\":6,\"title\":{\"en\":\"\\u201cDigiuth\\u201d onlayn t\\u0259lim platformas\\u0131n\\u0131n a\\u00e7\\u0131l\\u0131\\u015f m\\u0259rasimi ba\\u015f tutub\",\"az\":\"On 1 June the Launch Ceremony of Digiuth Online Platform was held at ADA University\"},\"image\":\"9YO0VGDAT8rtkUskosboXjPdwY881XLtAa4DWEQ8.jpg\",\"tags\":\"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Digiuth\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"ESN Azerbaijan\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Onlayn T\\u0259lim\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"A\\u00e7\\u0131l\\u0131\\u015f m\\u0259rasimi\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Vi\\u015feqrad\\\"}]\",\"content_az\":\"<p><span>1 iyun 2022-ci il tarixind\\u0259 \\u201cErasmus T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259 \\u015e\\u0259b\\u0259k\\u0259si \\u2013 Az\\u0259rbaycan\\u201d ictimai birliyi t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n ADA Universitetind\\u0259 Beyn\\u0259lxalq Vi\\u015feqrad Fondu t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n maliyy\\u0259l\\u0259\\u015f\\u0259n \\u201cDigiuth\\u201d onlayn t\\u0259lim platformas\\u0131n\\u0131n a\\u00e7\\u0131l\\u0131\\u015f m\\u0259rasimi ba\\u015f tutub. Birliyin s\\u0259dri \\u018fli Ta\\u011f\\u0131yev t\\u0259dbiri a\\u00e7\\u0131q elan etdikd\\u0259n sonra r\\u0259q\\u0259msal \\u00f6yr\\u0259nm\\u0259nin, innovasiyalar\\u0131n g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r sektorunda v\\u0259 qeyri-formal t\\u0259hsilin inki\\u015faf\\u0131nda artan rolundan s\\u00f6z a\\u00e7\\u0131b. \\u201cDigiuth\\u201d layih\\u0259sinin \\u0259sas h\\u0259d\\u0259finin&nbsp; \\u00f6lk\\u0259mizd\\u0259 h\\u0259r bir g\\u0259nc \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn r\\u0259q\\u0259msal \\u00f6yr\\u0259nm\\u0259ni \\u0259l\\u00e7atan etm\\u0259kd\\u0259n ibar\\u0259t oldu\\u011fu qeyd ed\\u0259n \\u018fli Ta\\u011f\\u0131yev layih\\u0259y\\u0259 g\\u00f6st\\u0259rdiyi d\\u0259st\\u0259y\\u0259 g\\u00f6r\\u0259 layih\\u0259nin t\\u0259r\\u0259fda\\u015flar\\u0131na v\\u0259 Beyn\\u0259lxalq Vi\\u015feqrad Fonduna \\u00f6z t\\u0259\\u015f\\u0259kk\\u00fcr\\u00fcn\\u00fc bildirib. Daha sonra \\u00e7\\u0131x\\u0131\\u015f ed\\u0259n Macar\\u0131stan\\u0131n Az\\u0259rbaycandak\\u0131 s\\u0259firliyinin m\\u0259d\\u0259niyy\\u0259t v\\u0259 t\\u0259hsil \\u00fczr\\u0259 diplomat\\u0131 Mihaly Gruber i\\u015ftirak\\u00e7\\u0131lara Beyn\\u0259lxalq Vi\\u015feqrad Fondu haqq\\u0131nda \\u0259trafl\\u0131 m\\u0259lumat verib v\\u0259 fondun yaratd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 imkanlar\\u0131n Az\\u0259rbaycan v\\u0259 Vi\\u015feqrad qrupundan olan \\u00f6lk\\u0259l\\u0259r aras\\u0131nda \\u0259m\\u0259kda\\u015fl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n g\\u00fccl\\u0259ndirilm\\u0259sind\\u0259 rolunun \\u0259h\\u0259miyy\\u0259tini vur\\u011fulay\\u0131b. Daha sonra is\\u0259 \\u201cDigiuth\\u201d layih\\u0259sinin idar\\u0259etm\\u0259 qrupunun \\u00fczvl\\u0259ri olan Orduxan Q\\u0259hr\\u0259manzad\\u0259 v\\u0259 Heyd\\u0259r Rzayev platforman\\u0131n g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rl\\u0259 i\\u015f sah\\u0259sin\\u0259 m\\u00fchim bir yenilik g\\u0259tir\\u0259c\\u0259yini qeyd edib, layih\\u0259 haqq\\u0131nda hesabat verib, platforman\\u0131n g\\u0259l\\u0259c\\u0259k missiyas\\u0131, h\\u0259d\\u0259fl\\u0259ri bar\\u0259sind\\u0259 i\\u015ftirak\\u00e7\\u0131lar\\u0131 m\\u0259lumatland\\u0131r\\u0131b v\\u0259 maraql\\u0131 t\\u0259r\\u0259fl\\u0259ri \\u0259m\\u0259kda\\u015fl\\u0131\\u011fa d\\u0259v\\u0259t edibl\\u0259r.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: justify\\\"><span>S\\u00f6z\\u00fcged\\u0259n a\\u00e7\\u0131l\\u0131\\u015f m\\u0259rasimi birliyin milli prezidenti Ramiyy\\u0259 \\u015eahg\\u0259ldiyevan\\u0131n moderatorlu\\u011funda ba\\u015f tutub. T\\u0259dbird\\u0259 d\\u00f6vl\\u0259t qurumlar\\u0131n\\u0131n, Vi\\u015feqrad qrupundan olan \\u00f6lk\\u0259l\\u0259rin s\\u0259firlikl\\u0259rinin v\\u0259 g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlar\\u0131n\\u0131n n\\u00fcmay\\u0259nd\\u0259l\\u0259ri i\\u015ftirak edibl\\u0259r. M\\u0259rasimin r\\u0259smi hiss\\u0259sind\\u0259n sonra \\u00e7ay fasil\\u0259si t\\u0259\\u015fkil olunub v\\u0259 Macar\\u0131stan\\u0131n \\u00f6lk\\u0259mizd\\u0259ki s\\u0259firliyinin d\\u0259st\\u0259yi il\\u0259 az\\u0259rbaycanl\\u0131 fotoqraflar\\u0131n Vi\\u015feqrad qrupundan olan \\u00f6lk\\u0259l\\u0259rd\\u0259 \\u00e7\\u0259kdikl\\u0259ri fotolar s\\u0259rgil\\u0259nib.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: justify\\\"><span>Xat\\u0131rladaq ki, Erasmus T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259 \\u015e\\u0259b\\u0259k\\u0259sinin Az\\u0259rbaycan n\\u00fcmay\\u0259nd\\u0259liyi&nbsp; 2016-ci ild\\u0259 t\\u0259\\u015f\\u0259bb\\u00fcs qrupu olaraq yarad\\u0131l\\u0131b, 2019-cu ild\\u0259 is\\u0259 r\\u0259smi qeydiyyata al\\u0131n\\u0131b. Birliyin \\u0259sas f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t sah\\u0259si g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rin Erasmus+ v\\u0259 dig\\u0259r proqramlar vasit\\u0259si il\\u0259 xaricd\\u0259 t\\u0259hsil almas\\u0131na v\\u0259 t\\u0259cr\\u00fcb\\u0259 qazanmas\\u0131na d\\u0259st\\u0259k olmaq, Erasmus+ proqram\\u0131n\\u0131n m\\u0259zunlar\\u0131 aras\\u0131nda \\u0259laq\\u0259 yaratmaq, beyn\\u0259lxalq k\\u00f6n\\u00fcll\\u00fcl\\u00fck proqramlar\\u0131n\\u0131 t\\u0259\\u015fviq etm\\u0259k, inkluziv t\\u0259hsilin inki\\u015faf\\u0131na t\\u00f6hf\\u0259 verm\\u0259k, \\u0259cn\\u0259bi t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259rin (g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rin) \\u00f6lk\\u0259mizd\\u0259 sosial v\\u0259 m\\u0259d\\u0259ni&nbsp; inteqrasiyas\\u0131na yard\\u0131m etm\\u0259kd\\u0259n ibar\\u0259tdir.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"content\":\"<p>On June 1, 2022, the Launch Ceremony of Digiuth Online Learning platform was held at ADA University by the \\u201cErasmus Student Network - Azerbaijan\\u201d public union. Chairman of the union Ali Tagiyev opened the event with an introductory speech and stressed the growing role of digital learning, innovations, and importance of digital non-formal education in development of the youth sector. Mihaly Gruber, Diplomat for Culture and Education at Hungarian Embassy in Baku, informed the participants about the mission of the International Visegrad Foundation and highligthed the importance of the opportunities created by the foundation in strengthening cooperation between Azerbaijan and the Visegrad group of countries. Ordukhan Gahramanzade and Heydar Rzayev, members of the management team of the \\u201cDigiuth\\u201d project, noted that the platform will bring significant innovation in the field of youth work by giving a detailed report on the project. Participants were informed about the future mission and goals of the platform and and interested parties were nvited to cooperate in the future as well. The launch ceremony was moderated by the National President of ESN Azerbaijan Ramiyya Shahgeldiyeva.<\\/p><p>The Digiuth project is co-financed by the Governments of Czechia, Hungary, Poland, and Slovakia through Visegrad Grants from International Visegrad Fund. The mission of the fund is to advance ideas for sustainable regional cooperation in Central Europe.<\\/p>\",\"user_id\":\"10\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-06-04T14:37:10.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-06-04T14:37:10.000000Z\",\"id\":6}'),
