(58, '{\"en\":\"The video tutorial provides information about Front-end Web-Development. After getting acquainted with languages such as HTML, CSS, JS, you will learn where and how to use them. In the final stage, with the help of what you have learned, you will create a website related to the constellations. In the end, you will get your certificate by answering the quiz questions.\",\"az\":\"Video d\\u0259rslikd\\u0259 Front-end Web-Development haqq\\u0131nda m\\u0259lumatlar verilir. HTML, CSS, JS kimi dill\\u0259rl\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f olduqdan sonra onlar\\u0131 harada v\\u0259 nec\\u0259 istifad\\u0259 etm\\u0259li oldu\\u011fumuzu \\u00f6yr\\u0259nirsiniz. Son m\\u0259rh\\u0259l\\u0259d\\u0259 is\\u0259 \\u00f6yr\\u0259ndikl\\u0259rinizin k\\u00f6m\\u0259yi il\\u0259 b\\u00fcrcl\\u0259rl\\u0259 \\u0259laq\\u0259li bir vebsayt quracaqs\\u0131n\\u0131z. Sonda is\\u0259 quiz suallar\\u0131n\\u0131 cavabland\\u0131raraq sertifikat\\u0131n\\u0131z\\u0131 \\u0259ld\\u0259 ed\\u0259c\\u0259ksiniz.\"}', 'Azərbaycan dili', '120 dəqiqə', 11, 4, 61, 15, '{\"en\":\"Introduction to HTML\",\"az\":\"HTML-\\u0259 giri\\u015f\"}', '9vkOONZmoRWFEbzrMt2VOw2FtZVgQIu6T7VK7kHJ.png', '{\"en\":\"<div>The video tutorial provides information about Front-end Web-Development. After getting acquainted with languages such as HTML, CSS, JS, you will learn where and how to use them. In the final stage, with the help of what you have learned, you will create a website related to the constellations. In the end, you will get your certificate by answering the quiz questions.<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>Video d\\u0259rslikd\\u0259 Front-end Web-Development haqq\\u0131nda m\\u0259lumatlar verilir. HTML, CSS, JS kimi dill\\u0259rl\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f olduqdan sonra onlar\\u0131 harada v\\u0259 nec\\u0259 istifad\\u0259 etm\\u0259li oldu\\u011fumuzu \\u00f6yr\\u0259nirsiniz. Son m\\u0259rh\\u0259l\\u0259d\\u0259 is\\u0259 \\u00f6yr\\u0259ndikl\\u0259rinizin k\\u00f6m\\u0259yi il\\u0259 b\\u00f