(4, '{\"en\":\"Launch Ceremony of Digiuth Learning Platform\",\"az\":\"\\\"Digiuth\\\" onlayn t\\u0259lim platfromas\\u0131n\\u0131n a\\u00e7\\u0131l\\u0131\\u015f m\\u0259rasimi\"}', '{\"en\":\"Erasmus Student Network Azerbaijan\",\"az\":\"\\\"Eramus T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259 \\u015e\\u0259b\\u0259k\\u0259si - Az\\u0259rbaycan\\\" ictimai birliyi\"}', '{\"en\":\"ADA University\",\"az\":\"ADA Universiteti\"}', 'projects@esn.az', '{\"en\":\"It gives us a great pleasure to announce that Launch Ceremony of Digiuth Online Learning Platform is here! In the ceremony participants will get a chance to know more about the Digiuth project, its future perspectives that will be followed by Q&A session.\\r\\n\\r\\nDigiuth is a online learning platform coordinated by Erasmus Student Network Azerbaijan which brings the trainers specialized in various subjects and learners together.  The main goal of the project is to increase the online learning opportunities for the youth and youth organizations.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Digiuth project is co-financed by the Governments of Czechia, Hungary, Poland, and Slovakia through Visegrad Grants from International Visegrad Fund. The mission of the fund is to advance ideas for sustainable regional cooperation in Central Europe.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe event will take place on 1 June at 15:00 in the Majlis Room, ADA University \\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nRepresentatives of youth organizations can attend in the event. For registration please contact us at projects@esn.az\",\"az\":\"\\u201cDigiuth\\u201d Onlayn \\u00d6yr\\u0259nm\\u0259 Platformas\\u0131n\\u0131n a\\u00e7\\u0131l\\u0131\\u015f m\\u0259rasimini elan etm\\u0259kd\\u0259n q\\u00fcrur duyuruq! M\\u0259rasimd\\u0259 i\\u015ftirak\\u00e7\\u0131lar \\u201cDigiuth\\u201dlayih\\u0259si, onun g\\u0259l\\u0259c\\u0259k perspektivl\\u0259ri haqq\\u0131nda \\u0259trafl\\u0131 m\\u0259lumat \\u0259ld\\u0259 etm\\u0259k \\u015fans\\u0131 \\u0259ld\\u0259 ed\\u0259c\\u0259kdirl\\u0259r. Daha sonra is\\u0259 m\\u00f6vcud suallar\\u0131 cavabland\\u0131rmaq \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn sual-cavab sessiyas\\u0131 t\\u0259\\u015fkil olunacaqd\\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u201cDigiuth\\u201dm\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif sah\\u0259l\\u0259r \\u00fczr\\u0259 ixtisasla\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015f t\\u0259lim\\u00e7il\\u0259ri v\\u0259 inki\\u015faf etm\\u0259k ist\\u0259y\\u0259n g\\u0259ncl\\u0259ri bir araya g\\u0259tir\\u0259n v\\u0259 \\\"Erasmus T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259 \\u015e\\u0259b\\u0259k\\u0259si - Az\\u0259rbaycan\\\" ictimai birliyi t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n koordinasiya edil\\u0259n onlayn t\\u0259lim platformas\\u0131d\\u0131r. Layih\\u0259nin \\u0259sas m\\u0259qs\\u0259di g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rin v\\u0259 g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlar\\u0131n\\u0131n onlayn t\\u0259lim resurslar\\u0131n\\u0131n art\\u0131r\\u0131lmas\\u0131d\\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"Digiuth\\\" layih\\u0259si \\u00c7exiya, Macar\\u0131stan, Pol\\u015fa v\\u0259 Slovakiya h\\u00f6kum\\u0259tl\\u0259ri t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n Beyn\\u0259lxalq Vi\\u015feqrad Fondunun Vi\\u015feqrad qrantlar\\u0131 vasit\\u0259sil\\u0259 birg\\u0259 maliyy\\u0259l\\u0259\\u015fdirilir. Fondun \\u0259sas missiyas\\u0131 M\\u0259rk\\u0259zi Avropada davaml\\u0131 regional \\u0259m\\u0259kda\\u015fl\\u0131q \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn ideyalar\\u0131 t\\u0259\\u015fviq etm\\u0259kd\\u0259n ibar\\u0259tdir.\\r\\n\\r\\nS\\u00f6z\\u00fcged\\u0259n t\\u0259dbir 1 iyun saat 15:00-da ADA Universitetinin M\\u0259clis zal\\u0131nda ba\\u015f tutacaqd\\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nT\\u0259dbird\\u0259 g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlar\\u0131n\\u0131n n\\u00fcmay\\u0259nd\\u0259l\\u0259ri i\\u015ftirak ed\\u0259 bil\\u0259rl\\u0259r. Qeydiyyatdan ke\\u00e7m\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn projects@esn.az \\u00fcnvan\\u0131na m\\u00fcraci\\u0259t etm\\u0259yiniz xahi\\u015f olunur.\"}', '8razkwWwn7uTtlhsBn2FP6vdLQ3XAzM49Nj0KyFF.png', '2022-06-01 15:00:00', '+994517220085', 'www.digiuth.com', '2022-05-24 13:05:27', '2022-06-04 15:45:13');
