(14, '{\"en\":\"Ali Taghiyev\",\"az\":\"\\u018fli Ta\\u011f\\u0131yev\"}', '{\"en\":\"Project Team Lead\",\"az\":\"Layih\\u0259 r\\u0259hb\\u0259ri\"}', 'tAAJdQ5KkpzbgKOFBmCJZHQGwQ8txxDQvLiUhEsq.jpg', '{\"en\":\"<div>Ali Tagiyev received his bachelor\'s degree in International Studies from ADA University in Azerbaijan. During his bachelor studies, he participated in an exchange program at Vytautas Magnus University in Lithuania. In the following, he took part in the internship program at German International Cooperation Agency (GIZ) in Baku. During his bachelor studies Mr. Taghiyev has been actively involved in the organisation of several local and international events\\/projects. He has been working in the youth sector since 2019 serving as the chairperson of the \\\"Erasmus Student Network - Azerbaijan\\\" public union. Meanwhile, Ali Taghiyev has participated in the training program named \\\"#ErasmusUpgrade Training and Conference\\\" held in Brussels, Belgium with the support of the European Commission. Mr. Taghiyev is currently studying Master of Public Administration at ADA University with a Graduate Assistantship scholarship, and he works as a leading specialist in the Innovations in Education divison of the Institute of Education of the Republic of Azerbaijan under Ministry of Education. He is Project Lead of Digiuth Online Learning Platform. His main motivation is to make online learning accessible for every youth in Azerbaijan.<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>\\u018fli Ta\\u011f\\u0131yev ADA Universitetind\\u0259 Beyn\\u0259lxalq m\\u00fcnasib\\u0259tl\\u0259r ixtisas\\u0131 \\u00fczr\\u0259 bakalavr t\\u0259hsili alm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Bakalavr t\\u0259hsili m\\u00fcdd\\u0259tind\\u0259 Litvada yerl\\u0259\\u015f\\u0259n Vitatus Maqnus Universitetind\\u0259 m\\u00fcbadil\\u0259 proqram\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. Almaniya Beyn\\u0259lxalq \\u018fm\\u0259kda\\u015fl\\u0131q C\\u0259miyy\\u0259tinin (GIZ) Bak\\u0131 ofisind\\u0259 t\\u0259cr\\u00fcb\\u0259 proqram\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. Bir \\u00e7ox yerli v\\u0259 beyn\\u0259lxalq t\\u0259dbirl\\u0259rin\\/layih\\u0259l\\u0259rin i\\u015ftirak\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131 v\\u0259 t\\u0259\\u015fkilat\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131 olmu\\u015fdur. 2019-cu il-d\\u0259n g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r sektorunda f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259rir, \\u201cErasmus T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259 \\u015e\\u0259b\\u0259k\\u0259si \\u2013 Az\\u0259rbaycan\\u201d ictimai birliyinin s\\u0259dridir. Bel\\u00e7ikan\\u0131n Br\\u00fcssell \\u015f\\u0259h\\u0259rind\\u0259 Avropa Komissiyas\\u0131n\\u0131n d\\u0259st\\u0259yi il\\u0259 ba\\u015f tutan \\u201c#ErasmusUpgrade Training and Conference\\u201d adl\\u0131 beyn\\u0259lxalq t\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. Hal-haz\\u0131rda ADA Universitetind\\u0259 daxili t\\u0259dqiqat t\\u0259qa\\u00fcd\\u00fc (Graduate Assistantship)&nbsp; il\\u0259 \\u201cD\\u00f6vl\\u0259t idar\\u0259etm\\u0259si\\u201d ixtisas\\u0131 \\u00fczr\\u0259 magistr t\\u0259hsili al\\u0131r. Az\\u0259rbaycan Respublikas\\u0131n\\u0131n T\\u0259hsil \\u0130nstitutunun T\\u0259hsild\\u0259 innovasiyalar \\u015f\\u00f6b\\u0259sind\\u0259 apar\\u0131c\\u0131 m\\u00fct\\u0259x\\u0259ssis v\\u0259zif\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131r. Digiuth\\u201d onlayn t\\u0259lim platformas\\u0131 layih\\u0259sinin r\\u0259hb\\u0259ridir. Onun bu layih\\u0259y\\u0259 r\\u0259hb\\u0259rlik etm\\u0259kd\\u0259 \\u0259sas h\\u0259d\\u0259fi m\\u0259saf\\u0259d\\u0259n qeyri-formal t\\u0259hsili \\u00f6lk\\u0259mizd\\u0259 h\\u0259r bir g\\u0259nc \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\u0259l\\u00e7atan etm\\u0259kdir.<br><br><\\/div>\"}', 'https://www.facebook.com/alitaghiyevv/', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/alitaghiyev/?originalSubdomain=az', '2022-05-31 15:05:00', '2023-03-07 21:55:17'),
(15, '{\"en\":\"Heydar Rzayev\",\"az\":\"Heyd\\u0259r Rzayev\"}', '{\"en\":\"Project Manager\",\"az\":\"Layih\\u0259 meneceri\"}', 'mo8wFKLqMEje0UImO0w1efB0Snp1WKUbw71jGID4.jpg', '{\"en\":\"<div>Heydar Rzayev graduated from ADA University with a degree in International Relations in 2020. Since 2019, he has worked as a board member and project manager at the Erasmus Student Network public union, which operates in the field of higher education. During his tenure, he won and implemented grants from various organizations such as ESAA, Visegrad and ESN International. Heydar Rzayev, who is currently pursuing a master\'s degree as an Erasmus Mundus scholar, worked as an intern at the UNESCO Institute for Lifelong Learning and the Agency for Quality Assurance in Education of the Republic of the Azerbaijan. He is currently working as a leading specialist in the Department of Strategic Research in Education of the Institute of Education of the Republic of Azerbaijan. When writing Digiuth project, Heydar\\u2019s main goal was to increase the access of Azerbaijani youth, especially young people living in our regions, to additional\\/ extracurricular education. He hopes that Digiuth will achieve his goal and play a major role in the personal development of young people of Azerbaijan.<br><br><\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>Heyd\\u0259r Rzayev 2020-ci ild\\u0259 ADA Universitetinin Beyn\\u0259lxalq M\\u00fcnasib\\u0259tl\\u0259r fak\\u00fclt\\u0259sini bitirmi\\u015fdir. 2019-cu ild\\u0259n ali t\\u0259hsil sah\\u0259sind\\u0259 f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259r\\u0259n \\\"Erasmus T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259 T\\u0259\\u015fkilat\\u0131\\\" ictimai birliyind\\u0259 idar\\u0259 hey\\u0259tinin \\u00fczv\\u00fc v\\u0259 layih\\u0259 meneceri v\\u0259zif\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. F\\u0259aliyy\\u0259td\\u0259 oldu\\u011fu m\\u00fcdd\\u0259td\\u0259 o, \\\"ESAA\\\", \\\"Visegrad\\\" v\\u0259 \\\"ESN International\\\" kimi m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlardan qrantlar qazanm\\u0131\\u015f v\\u0259 h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7irmi\\u015fdir. Haz\\u0131rda magistratura pill\\u0259sind\\u0259 t\\u0259hsilini \\\"Erasmus Mundus\\\" t\\u0259qa\\u00fcd\\u00e7\\u00fcs\\u00fc olaraq davam etdir\\u0259n Heyd\\u0259r Rzayev t\\u0259hsil ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 d\\u00f6vrd\\u0259 YUNESKO \\u00d6m\\u00fcr Boyu T\\u0259hshil \\u0130nstitutunda v\\u0259 Az\\u0259rbaycan Respublikas\\u0131n\\u0131n T\\u0259hsild\\u0259 Keyfiyy\\u0259t T\\u0259minat\\u0131 Agentliyind\\u0259&nbsp; t\\u0259cr\\u00fcb\\u0259\\u00e7i olaraq \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Hal-haz\\u0131rda Az\\u0259rbaycan Respublikas\\u0131n\\u0131n T\\u0259hsil \\u0130nstitutunun T\\u0259hsild\\u0259 strateji t\\u0259dqiqatlar \\u015f\\u00f6b\\u0259sind\\u0259 apar\\u0131c\\u0131 m\\u00fct\\u0259x\\u0259ssis v\\u0259zif\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131r. Heyd\\u0259rin Digiuth proyektini yazark\\u0259n \\u0259sas m\\u0259qs\\u0259di Az\\u0259rbaycan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rinin x\\u00fcsusil\\u0259 d\\u0259 b\\u00f6lg\\u0259l\\u0259rimizd\\u0259 ya\\u015fayan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rin \\u0259lav\\u0259\\/m\\u0259kt\\u0259bd\\u0259nk\\u0259nar t\\u0259hsil\\u0259 \\u00e7\\u0131x\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131n\\u0131 art\\u0131rmaq idi. O, \\u00fcmid edir ki, Digiuth \\u00f6z m\\u0259qs\\u0259din\\u0259 \\u00e7atacaq v\\u0259 Az\\u0259rbaycan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rinin \\u015f\\u0259xsi inki\\u015faf\\u0131nda b\\u00f6y\\u00fck rol oynayacaq.&nbsp;<br><br><\\/div>\"}', 'https://www.facebook.com/r.heydar85', 'https://www.instagram.com/heydar_r_/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/heydar-rzayev-21a08018a/', '2023-03-07 21:53:28', '2023-03-07 21:53:28');
INSERT INTO `testimonials` (`id`, `fullname`, `position`, `image`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, '{\"en\":\"Azer Aliyev\",\"az\":\"Az\\u0259r \\u018fliyev\"}', '{\"en\":\"Chairman of NAYORA\",\"az\":\"ARGTM\\u015e-nin s\\u0259dri\"}', 'dtakn3xE6fw6GGyo0ZPEdiDTPUx4HQtDD5YTIYb9.jpg', '{\"en\":\"Digiuth is a unique online platform aimed at increasing the digital learning resources for youth organizations and youth in Azerbaijan. In particular, at a time when digitalization is becoming significantly important, the opportunities created by this platform for young people are very beneficial. The free online courses provided by the young professionals make this platform more inclusive and accessible to the young people from different social backgrounds. Meanwhile, it is worth to mention that the platform is very user friendly for the young generation.\",\"az\":\"\\\"Digiuth\\\" Az\\u0259rbaycanda g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlar\\u0131 v\\u0259 g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn r\\u0259q\\u0259msal \\u00f6yr\\u0259nm\\u0259 resurslar\\u0131n\\u0131n art\\u0131r\\u0131lmas\\u0131na y\\u00f6n\\u0259lmi\\u015f unikal onlayn \\u015f\\u0259xsi inki\\u015faf platformas\\u0131d\\u0131r. X\\u00fcsusil\\u0259 d\\u0259 r\\u0259q\\u0259msalla\\u015fman\\u0131n getdikc\\u0259 aktualla\\u015fd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 bir d\\u00f6vrd\\u0259 bu platforman\\u0131n g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn yaratd\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 imkanlar \\u00e7ox faydal\\u0131 v\\u0259 \\u0259v\\u0259zedilm\\u0259zdir. G\\u0259nc m\\u00fct\\u0259x\\u0259ssisl\\u0259r t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n t\\u0259qdim edil\\u0259n pulsuz onlayn kurslar bu platforman\\u0131 m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif sosial kateqoriyalardan olan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\u0259hat\\u0259li v\\u0259 \\u0259l\\u00e7atan edir. H\\u0259m\\u00e7inin, platforman\\u0131n xidm\\u0259tl\\u0259rind\\u0259n istifad\\u0259 etm\\u0259k g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn asan v\\u0259 rahatd\\u0131r.\"}', '2022-02-09 08:51:11', '2022-05-30 03:26:11');
