(14, NULL, NULL, '{\"en\":\"Tangiz Alizada\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259ngiz \\u018flizad\\u0259\"}', '{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"}', 'qwUy1i5NGC4Y2fvtSYuh0ohByq5CDzIRnWe2ehk8.jpg', '{\"az\":\"<div>T\\u0259ngiz \\u018flizad\\u0259 haz\\u0131rda ADA Universitetind\\u0259 \\u0130nformasiya texnologiyalar\\u0131 ixtisas\\u0131 \\u00fczr\\u0259 bakalavr t\\u0259hsili al\\u0131r. T\\u0259ngiz b\\u0259yin ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 t\\u0259hsil n\\u0259tic\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\\"front-end development\\\"-\\u0259 olan mara\\u011f\\u0131 daha da art\\u0131b v\\u0259 HTML, CSS, JS \\u00fczr\\u0259 \\u00f6z bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131n\\u0131 daha da inki\\u015faf etdirib.<br>T\\u0259ngiz \\u018flizad\\u0259 layih\\u0259miz \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 beyn\\u0259lxalq ekspertl\\u0259r t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n \\u201cDelve into the World of IT \\u201d v\\u0259 \\u201dBuild Your Own Websit \\\" m\\u00f6vzular\\u0131nda t\\u0259liml\\u0259r ke\\u00e7ib v\\u0259 Digiuth platformas\\u0131 \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\\"HTML\\\" il\\u0259 proqramla\\u015fd\\u0131rmaya giri\\u015f adl\\u0131 onlayn t\\u0259lim kursu haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.<br>T\\u0259ngiz \\u018flizad\\u0259nin \\u201cDigiuth\\u201d layih\\u0259sin\\u0259 qo\\u015fulmas\\u0131n\\u0131n \\u0259sas s\\u0259b\\u0259bi veb sayt qurma \\u00fczr\\u0259 olan bilik v\\u0259 bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131n\\u0131 inki\\u015faf etdirm\\u0259k v\\u0259 bu i\\u015f\\u0259 h\\u0259v\\u0259si olan dig\\u0259r insanlara d\\u0259st\\u0259k olmaqdan ibar\\u0259tdir. \\u201cDigiuth\\u201dkomandas\\u0131 t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n t\\u0259\\u015fkil edil\\u0259n 2 h\\u0259ft\\u0259lik t\\u0259liml\\u0259r\\u0259 qat\\u0131laraq T\\u0259ngiz \\u018flizad\\u0259 \\u00f6z bilik v\\u0259 bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131n\\u0131 daha da art\\u0131rma\\u011fa nail olub. Haz\\u0131rlad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 materiallar\\u0131n dig\\u0259r insanlara \\u201cfront-end\\u201d proqramla\\u015fd\\u0131rman\\u0131 geni\\u015f v\\u0259 detall\\u0131 \\u015f\\u0259kild\\u0259 izah ed\\u0259c\\u0259yini v\\u0259 insanlar\\u0131n bu m\\u0259lumatlardan istifad\\u0259 ed\\u0259r\\u0259k yeni bilik v\\u0259 bacar\\u0131qlara yiy\\u0259l\\u0259n\\u0259c\\u0259yini d\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcnm\\u0259k onu h\\u0259y\\u0259canland\\u0131ran \\u0259sas m\\u0259qamlardan biridir. O, g\\u0259l\\u0259c\\u0259kd\\u0259 \\u201cDiguth\\u201dun Az\\u0259rbaycan\\u0131n g\\u0259ncl\\u0259ri \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn yaradaca\\u011f\\u0131 f\\u00fcrs\\u0259tl\\u0259ri s\\u0259birsizlikl\\u0259 g\\u00f6zl\\u0259yir.<\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>Tangiz Alizada is currently studying for a bachelor\'s degree in Information Technology at ADA University. As a result of his studies, Mr. Alizade has became more interested in front-end development and developed his HTML, CAS, JS skills. Within the Digiuth project Mr. Alizade has been trained on \\\"Delve into the World of IT\\\" and \\\"Build Your Own Website \\\" by our international experts. Mr. Alizade has prepared the online course entitled \\\"Introduction to HTML\\\" for the Digiuth platform during this project.<br>The main reason that Tangiz Alizade joined the Diguth program was to develop his knowledge and skills in building a website and to help other people who are interested in this field. After participating in a two weeks training organized by the Digiuth team and mastering what to do, his interest in this field increased even more. One of the main things that excites him is that he thinks that his study materials will explain the front-end development to other&nbsp; interested people in a broad and detailed way, and that people will use this information to acquire new knowledge and skills. Mr. Alizada is looking forward to the future opportunities that Diguth will create to the youth of Azerbaijan.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\"}', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/tangiz-alizada-00487b190/', '2022-04-08 01:19:55', '2022-04-17 04:14:01'),
(15, NULL, NULL, '{\"en\":\"Ali Aliyev\",\"az\":\"\\u018fli \\u018fliyev\"}', '{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"}', 'PIkDzzj0gsJQhaonHuiDk6kL08XV1IFqNLzAT5ZH.jpg', '{\"en\":\"<div>Ali Aliyev is a 3rd-year computer science student at ADA University. He is currently studying at KAIST University in the Republic of Korea with an exchange program. During his university life, he has participated in various social and academic events. He is also part of the ADA ACM organization. He also worked as a teaching assistant for the programming course at ADA University. His dream is to work at one of the Silicon Valley companies. Ali prepared \\u201cIntroduction to C Programming Language\\u201d video lessons for the Digiuth platform to help others to achieve their goals.&nbsp;<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div><strong>\\u018fli \\u018fliyev<\\/strong> ADA Universitetinin 3-c\\u00fc kurs Kompyuter Elml\\u0259ri t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259sidir. Hal- haz\\u0131rda t\\u0259hsilini M\\u00fcbadil\\u0259 Proqram\\u0131 vasit\\u0259sil\\u0259 Koreya respublikas\\u0131n\\u0131n KA\\u0130ST Universitetind\\u0259 d\\u0259vam etdirir. Universitet h\\u0259yat\\u0131 boyunca sosial ve elmi bir \\u00e7ox proqramlarda i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. Eyni zamanda, \\u201dADA ACM\\u201d&nbsp; t\\u0259\\u015fkilat\\u0131n\\u0131n \\u00fczv\\u00fcd\\u00fcr. Bundan \\u0259lav\\u0259,&nbsp; ADA Universitetind\\u0259 Proqramla\\u015fd\\u0131rma dili d\\u0259rsind\\u0259 m\\u00fc\\u0259llim k\\u00f6m\\u0259k\\u00e7isi kimi i\\u015fl\\u0259mi\\u015fdir. \\u018fn b\\u00f6y\\u00fck arzusu is\\u0259 g\\u0259l\\u0259c\\u0259kd\\u0259 \\\"Silikon Vadisi\\\" \\u015firk\\u0259tl\\u0259rinin birind\\u0259 i\\u015fl\\u0259m\\u0259kdir. \\u018fli ba\\u015fqalar\\u0131na da m\\u0259qs\\u0259dl\\u0259rin\\u0259 \\u00e7atmaqda k\\u00f6m\\u0259k etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn Digiuth platformas\\u0131 \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\u201cC Proqramla\\u015fd\\u0131rma Dilin\\u0259 Giri\\u015f\\u201d video d\\u0259rsl\\u0259ri haz\\u0131rlad\\u0131.<\\/div>\"}', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ali-aliyev-44368117b/', '2022-04-08 01:20:39', '2022-04-17 04:11:25'),
(16, NULL, NULL, '{\"en\":\"Etibar Khidirov\",\"az\":\"Etibar X\\u0131d\\u0131rov\"}', '{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"}', 'fM8zi93knn78a2tHE3ymjf4txVpYBtNuMX0cnyPx.jpg', '{\"az\":\"<div>Etibar X\\u0131d\\u0131rov&nbsp; X\\u0259z\\u0259r universitetinin \\u0130qtisadiyyat v\\u0259 Menecment&nbsp; fak\\u00fclt\\u0259si m\\u0259zunudur. Universitet ill\\u0259rind\\u0259n \\u00f6lk\\u0259d\\u0259 h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7iril\\u0259n bir \\u00e7ox b\\u00f6y\\u00fck forum v\\u0259 t\\u0259dbirl\\u0259rd\\u0259 k\\u00f6n\\u00fcll\\u00fc v\\u0259 k\\u00f6n\\u00fcll\\u00fcl\\u0259r \\u00fczr\\u0259 koordinator kimi f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259tl\\u0259ri olub.&nbsp; Bundan \\u0259lav\\u0259, bir \\u00e7ox sosial layih\\u0259l\\u0259rin aktiv i\\u015ftirak\\u00e7\\u0131s\\u0131 v\\u0259 t\\u0259\\u015fkilat\\u00e7\\u0131lar\\u0131ndan biri olmu\\u015fdur.&nbsp; Sosial layih\\u0259l\\u0259rd\\u0259 i\\u015ftirak onda daha sonra sosial sahibkarl\\u0131\\u011fa maraq oyatm\\u0131\\u015f v\\u0259 bu sah\\u0259 \\u00fczr\\u0259 maraqlanma\\u011fa v\\u0259 ara\\u015fd\\u0131rmalar etm\\u0259y\\u0259 ba\\u015flam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.&nbsp; El\\u0259 ilk karyeras\\u0131na da 4-c\\u00fc kursda t\\u0259hsil alark\\u0259n Sosial Sahibkarl\\u0131q Modeli \\u0259sas\\u0131nda f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259r\\u0259n \\u00f6lk\\u0259nin ilk kraudfandinq platformas\\u0131 Toxum.org-da layih\\u0259l\\u0259r \\u00fczr\\u0259 menecer kimi ba\\u015flam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Etibar sosial sahibkarl\\u0131qla tan\\u0131\\u015f olduqdan sonra bu sah\\u0259d\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fmaqdan z\\u00f6vq ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n h\\u0259m\\u00e7inin, bu sah\\u0259nin \\u015f\\u0259xsi d\\u0259y\\u0259rl\\u0259ri il\\u0259 \\u00fcst-\\u00fcst\\u0259 d\\u00fc\\u015fd\\u00fcy\\u00fcn\\u00fcn f\\u0259rqin\\u0259 vard\\u0131 . N\\u0259hay\\u0259t, 2022-ci ild\\u0259 Etibar \\u00f6z\\u00fcn\\u00fcn bu m\\u0259qs\\u0259dini realla\\u015fd\\u0131rd\\u0131. \\u00d6lk\\u0259d\\u0259 olan sosial v\\u0259 sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q layih\\u0259l\\u0259rinin resurs ehtiyac\\u0131n\\u0131 qar\\u015f\\u0131lamaqda onlara d\\u0259st\\u0259k olacaq \\\"D\\u0259st\\u0259k\\u00e7i\\\" (Destekchi.org) Sosial Sahibkarl\\u0131q Platformas\\u0131n\\u0131 qurdu.&nbsp; Etibar\\u0131n g\\u0259l\\u0259c\\u0259k planlar\\u0131 Az\\u0259rbaycanda yeni inki\\u015faf etm\\u0259y\\u0259 ba\\u015flayan sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q sah\\u0259si \\u00fczr\\u0259 bacard\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 q\\u0259d\\u0259r \\u00f6z t\\u00f6hf\\u0259sini verm\\u0259k v\\u0259 bu sah\\u0259y\\u0259 ba\\u015flamaq ist\\u0259y\\u0259nl\\u0259r\\u0259 d\\u0259st\\u0259k olmaqd\\u0131r. Az\\u0259rbaycandak\\u0131 sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q il\\u0259 maraqlananlara t\\u00f6hv\\u0259 verm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn Digiuth proyekti \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u201cSosial sahibkarl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n \\u0259saslar\\u201d adl\\u0131 video d\\u0259rslik haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>Etibar Khidirov is a graduate of Khazar University\'s faculty of Economics and Management.&nbsp; Since his university years, he has served as a volunteer and volunteer coordinator at many major forums and events in the country.&nbsp; In addition, he was an active participant and organizer of many social projects.&nbsp; Participation in social projects later aroused interest in Social Entrepreneurship and he began to take an interest in and research in this area.&nbsp; When he was in his 4th year, he started his career as a project manager at Toxum.org, the country\'s first crowdfunding platform based on the Social Entrepreneurship model.&nbsp; After getting acquainted with social entrepreneurship,&nbsp; his goal was to build his own social entrepreneurship project to benefit society more. Etibar achieved his goal in 2022.&nbsp; Destekchi.org has established the Social Entrepreneurship Platform, which will support social entrepreneurship projects in the country to meet their resource needs.&nbsp; Future plans of the Etibar are to contribute as much as possible to the newly developed field of social entrepreneurship in Azerbaijan and to support those who want to start in this field. He has developed a video lesson&nbsp; entitled \\\"Fundamentals of Social Entrepreneurship\\\" as part of the Digiuth project to contribute to those interested in social entrepreneurship in Azerbaijan.<\\/div>\"}', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/etibar-khidirov/', '2022-04-08 01:21:52', '2022-04-17 04:08:32'),
(17, NULL, NULL, '{\"en\":\"Fidan Ahmadli\",\"az\":\"Fidan \\u018fhm\\u0259dli\"}', '{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"}', 'iQRYWBCbtZDmdYvgEIhk4rmKBqxufZuPpH6AdO6m.jpg', '{\"en\":\"<div>Fidan Ahmadli graduated from the lyceum named after Academician Zarifa Aliyeva in 2015. She is a graduate of ADA University\'s Faculty of Computer Engineering. In 2019, she won the Erasmus + program and continued her education at Istanbul City University for 1 semester in January-May. In 2018, she won the Global Startup Lab program held by MIT University in Azerbaijan and participated in 6-week startup training organized by MIT. Fidan has many certifications, including \\u2018Oracle Certified Associate\\u2019. During her university years, she has participated in many internship programs, including Azersun Holding, TelecomInvest companies. Since September 2020, she has been working at Azerconnect LLC as a specialist in IT Corporate Platforms. Fidan prepared \\u201cIntroduction to SQL\\u201d video lessons for the Digiuth platform and hopes it will be useful for the youth who wants to delve into the world of IT.&nbsp;<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div><strong>Fidan \\u018fhm\\u0259dli <\\/strong>2015-ci ild\\u0259 Akademik Z\\u0259rif\\u0259 \\u018fliyeva ad\\u0131na liseyden m\\u0259zun olmu\\u015fdur. O, ADA Universitetinin Komp\\u00fcter M\\u00fch\\u0259nd\\u0259sliyi fak\\u00fclt\\u0259si m\\u0259zunudur. 2019-cu ild\\u0259 Erasmus+ proqram\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak etm\\u0259 haqq\\u0131 qazanm\\u0131\\u015f v\\u0259 h\\u0259min proqram \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 yanvar-may aylar\\u0131 \\u0259rzind\\u0259 1 semestr boyunca \\u0130stanbul \\u015eehir Universitetind\\u0259 t\\u0259hsilini davam etdirmi\\u015fdir. 2018-ci ild\\u0259 Amerikan\\u0131n MIT Universitetinin Az\\u0259rbaycanda ke\\u00e7irdiyi \\u201cGlobal Startup Lab\\u201d proqram\\u0131n\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak haqq\\u0131 qazanaraq, MIT t\\u0259r\\u0259find\\u0259n t\\u0259\\u015fkil olunan 6 h\\u0259ft\\u0259lik startup t\\u0259liml\\u0259rind\\u0259 i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. Fidan, \\u2018Oracle Certified Associated\\u2019 daxil olmaqla, bir \\u00e7ox sertifikatlar\\u0131n sahibidir. Universitet ill\\u0259ri boyunca \\u201cAzersun Holding\\u201d, \\u201cTelecomInvest\\u201d \\u015firk\\u0259tl\\u0259ri daxil olmaqla bir \\u00e7ox t\\u0259cr\\u00fcb\\u0259 proqramlar\\u0131nda i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. 2020-ci ilin Sentaybr ay\\u0131ndan etibar\\u0259n \\u201cAzerconnect\\u201d MMC-d\\u0259 IT Korperativ platformalar\\u0131 \\u00fczr\\u0259 m\\u00fct\\u0259x\\u0259ssis olaraq f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259rir. Fidan Digiuth platformas\\u0131 \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\u201cSQL-\\u0259 Giri\\u015f\\u201d video d\\u0259rsl\\u0259ri haz\\u0131rlad\\u0131 v\\u0259 bunun \\u0130T d\\u00fcnyas\\u0131na q\\u0259d\\u0259m qoyan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn faydal\\u0131 olaca\\u011f\\u0131na \\u00fcmid edir.<\\/div>\"}', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/fidan-ahmadli-46249a14b/', '2022-04-08 01:22:35', '2022-04-17 04:07:20'),
(18, NULL, NULL, '{\"en\":\"Gunay \\u0130smayilova\",\"az\":\"G\\u00fcnay \\u0130smay\\u0131lova\"}', '{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"}', 'cdHbsYfJd8eFjz0HRpmsEyWKjMxtdiyZq8LShzMh.jpg', '{\"en\":\"<div>Gunay Ismayilova<strong> <\\/strong>graduated from Baku State University, International Relations faculty. She is a proactive \\u201cEvent, Marketing &amp; Project\\u201d Manager, highly motivated, innovative, and result-oriented, focused on event, marketing and project planning strategies. She successfully delivered Games Event projects, Influencer Marketing projects in her career. Withing the Digiuth project she delivered \\u201cIntroduction to Project Management\\u201d video lessons for the proactive and enthusiastic youth of Azerbaijan.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>G\\u00fcnay \\u0130smay\\u0131lova Bak\\u0131 D\\u00f6vl\\u0259t Universitetinin Beyn\\u0259lxalq M\\u00fcnasib\\u0259tl\\u0259r fak\\u00fclt\\u0259sini bitirib. O, y\\u00fcks\\u0259k motivasiyal\\u0131, yenilik\\u00e7i v\\u0259 n\\u0259tic\\u0259y\\u00f6n\\u00fcml\\u00fc proaktiv \\u201cT\\u0259dbir, Marketinq v\\u0259 Layih\\u0259\\u201d meneceridir. \\u201cOyun T\\u0259dbir layih\\u0259l\\u0259ri\\u201d, \\u201cInfluencer Marketing\\u201d layih\\u0259l\\u0259rini u\\u011furla hayata ke\\u00e7irib. Digiuth layih\\u0259si \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 o, Az\\u0259rbaycan\\u0131n t\\u0259\\u015f\\u0259bb\\u00fcskar v\\u0259 h\\u0259v\\u0259sli g\\u0259ncl\\u0259ri \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\u201cLayih\\u0259l\\u0259rin idar\\u0259 edilm\\u0259sin\\u0259 giri\\u015f\\u201d video d\\u0259rsl\\u0259ri t\\u0259qdim etmi\\u015fdir.&nbsp;<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\"}', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/gunay-ismayilova-82192751/', '2022-04-08 01:23:31', '2022-04-17 04:04:25'),
