(20, NULL, NULL, '{\"en\":\"\\u0130lham Ahmadov\",\"az\":\"\\u0130lham \\u018fhm\\u0259dov\"}', '{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"}', 'IHHcvCpyUqaBnNdLm4rF9VrOpmVkbg3eOAx9SNCo.jpg', '{\"az\":\"<div><strong>\\u0130lham \\u018fhm\\u0259dov<\\/strong> bakalavr t\\u0259hsilini Amerikan\\u0131n \\u201dHartwick\\u201d Kollecind\\u0259 \\u0259ld\\u0259 etmi\\u015fdir. Bu layih\\u0259 \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u201c\\u0130\\u015fg\\u00fczar kommunikasiyan\\u0131n \\u0259saslar\\u0131 v\\u0259 idar\\u0259 edilm\\u0259si\\u201d m\\u00f6vzusunda video d\\u0259rslik&nbsp; haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Hal-haz\\u0131rda milli televiziyalar\\u0131n birind\\u0259 ba\\u015f redaktor v\\u0259zif\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131r. O, eyni zamanda pe\\u015f\\u0259kar t\\u0259rc\\u00fcm\\u0259\\u00e7idir v\\u0259 m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif m\\u00f6vzu v\\u0259 janrlarda ingilis-az\\u0259rbaycan-rus dill\\u0259rind\\u0259 yaz\\u0131l\\u0131 v\\u0259 \\u015fifahi t\\u0259rc\\u00fcm\\u0259l\\u0259r edir. O, \\u00fcmid edir ki, kursdan faydalananlar \\u00e7ox olacaq v\\u0259 burada \\u0259ld\\u0259 etdikl\\u0259ri bilikl\\u0259ri h\\u0259m pe\\u015f\\u0259kar h\\u0259yatlar\\u0131nda, h\\u0259m d\\u0259 \\u015f\\u0259xsi h\\u0259yatlar\\u0131nda t\\u0259tbiq ed\\u0259c\\u0259kl\\u0259r.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>Ilham Ahmadov received his bachelor\'s degree from Hartwick College in the United States. Within the framework of this project, he developed a course on the \\u201cBasics and Management of Business Communication\\u201d. He is currently the editor-in-chief of one of the national televisions. He is also a professional translator and provides written and oral translations in English-Azerbaijani-Russian on various topics and genres. He hopes that there will be many beneficiaries of the course and will apply the knowledge gained here both in their professional and personal lives.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><b