(164, 'İlkin Əziz', 'İlkin Aziz', NULL, 'elxan7891234@gmail.com', 'GCrHhArJOHW4Sti4V5hdOVOhB2PFaobBnZrN4o1y.pdf', NULL, 'teacher', '$2y$10$QSzAVNixgpExbRKwNPBtgOXD18IS7B7ghKxmIA5rsxrxOOCWjS86S', NULL, '2024-05-12 21:49:13', '2024-05-12 22:05:19', 'teacher', NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/ilkin-aziz/', 'https://www.instagram.com/ilkin-aziz/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ilkin-aziz/', '{\"az\":\"<p>\\u0130lkin \\u018fziz ADA Universitetinin Biznesin \\u0130dar\\u0259edilm\\u0259si fak&uuml;lt\\u0259si m\\u0259zunudur. Universitet ill\\u0259rind\\u0259n bir &ccedil;ox t\\u0259lim v\\u0259 konfranslarda i\\u015ftirak etmi\\u015fdir. O, universitetin 2-ci ilind\\u0259n etibar\\u0259n karyeras\\u0131n\\u0131n inki\\u015faf\\u0131 v\\u0259 planlamas\\u0131 &uuml;z\\u0259rind\\u0259 &ccedil;al\\u0131\\u015fma\\u011fa ba\\u015flay\\u0131b, &ldquo;Digital Services&rdquo;, &ldquo;Kibrit&rdquo; v\\u0259 &ldquo;AVAND Technology&rdquo; kimi m&uuml;xt\\u0259lif \\u015firk\\u0259tl\\u0259rd\\u0259 bilik v\\u0259 t\\u0259cr&uuml;b\\u0259 qazanm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Hal-haz\\u0131rda &rdquo;G-5 Group&rdquo; \\u015firk\\u0259tind\\u0259 Layih\\u0259l\\u0259r &uuml;zr\\u0259 menecer v\\u0259zif\\u0259sind\\u0259 f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g&ouml;st\\u0259rir, m&uuml;xt\\u0259lif y&ouml;nl\\u0259rd\\u0259 layih\\u0259l\\u0259r h\\u0259yata ke&ccedil;irir. Onun \\u0259n b&ouml;y&uuml;k m\\u0259qs\\u0259di u\\u011furlu bir m&uuml;t\\u0259x\\u0259ssis kimi inki\\u015faf edib, pe\\u015f\\u0259kar oldu\\u011fu sah\\u0259 &uuml;zr\\u0259 keyfiyy\\u0259tli t\\u0259liml\\u0259r ke&ccedil;\\u0259r\\u0259k m&uuml;t\\u0259x\\u0259ssisl\\u0259r yeti\\u015fdirm\\u0259kdir. Digiuth platformas\\u0131 &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n &ldquo;Qeyri-formal t\\u0259hsil n\\u0259dir?&rdquo; adl\\u0131 video d\\u0259rslik haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.<br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"en\":\"<p>Ilkin Aziz is a graduate of ADA University&#39;s Faculty of Business Administration. He has participated in many trainings and conferences since his university years. He has been working on career development and planning since the second year of university, gaining knowledge and experience in various companies such as Digital Services, &ldquo;Kibrit&rdquo; and AVAND Technology. He currently works as a Project Manager at G-5 Group, implementing projects in various fields. His biggest goal is to develop as a successful specialist and train specialists by providing quality training in the field in which he is a professional. He developed a video lesson called &quot;What is non-formal education?&quot; for the Digiuth platform.<br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}', '<p>İlkin Əziz ADA Universitetinin Biznesin İdarəedilməsi fak&uuml;ltəsi məzunudur. Universitet illərindən bir &ccedil;ox təlim və konfranslarda iştirak etmişdir. O, universitetin 2-ci ilindən etibarən karyerasının inkişafı və planlaması &uuml;zərində &ccedil;alışmağa başlayıb, &ldquo;Digital Services&rdquo;, &ldquo;Kibrit&rdquo; və &ldquo;AVAND Technology&rdquo; kimi m&uuml;xtəlif şirkətlərdə bilik və təcr&uuml;bə qazanmışdır. Hal-hazırda &rdquo;G-5 Group&rdquo; şirkətində Layihələr &uuml;zrə menecer vəzifəsində fəaliyyət g&ouml;stərir, m&uuml;xtəlif y&ouml;nlərdə layihələr həyata ke&ccedil;irir. Onun ən b&ouml;y&uuml;k məqsədi uğurlu bir m&uuml;təxəssis kimi inkişaf edib, peşəkar olduğu sahə &uuml;zrə keyfiyyətli təlimlər ke&ccedil;ərək m&uuml;təxəssislər yetişdirməkdir. Digiuth platforması &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n &ldquo;Qeyri-formal təhsil nədir?&rdquo; adlı video dərslik hazırlamışdır.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Ilkin Aziz is a graduate of ADA University&#39;s Faculty of Business Administration. He has participated in many trainings and conferences since his university years. He has been working on career development and planning since the second year of university, gaining knowledge and experience in various companies such as Digital Services, &ldquo;Kibrit&rdquo; and AVAND Technology. He currently works as a Project Manager at G-5 Group, implementing projects in various fields. His biggest goal is to develop as a successful specialist and train specialists by providing quality training in the field in which he is a professional. He developed a video lesson called &quot;What is non-formal education?&quot; for the Digiuth platform.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'ilkinaziz510', 'teacher', 1, '505100171'),
